      <title>随着挑战的增加，越南将优先考虑经济增长</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-20/vietnam-to-prioritize-economic-growth-as-challenges-mount</link>
      <description><![CDATA[越南副总理黎明凯表示，在全球需求疲软带来的持续挑战中，越南政府将优先支持经济增长。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-20/vietnam-to-prioritize-economic-growth-as-challenges-mount</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 20 May 2024 03:33:11 GMT</pubDate>
